<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en" class="h-full bg-slate-950">

<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>RakshaPath - Create Room</title>
    <!-- Tailwind CSS CDN -->
    <script src="https://cdn.tailwindcss.com"></script>
</head>

<body class="h-full flex items-center justify-center p-4 antialiased">

    <!-- Background glow elements -->
    <div
        class="absolute inset-0 bg-[radial-gradient(circle_at_top,rgba(16,185,129,0.06),transparent_50%)] pointer-events-none">
    </div>
    <div
        class="absolute inset-0 bg-[radial-gradient(circle_at_bottom,rgba(30,41,59,0.4),transparent_60%)] pointer-events-none">
    </div>

    <!-- Back Button to Map -->
    <a href="/map"
        class="absolute top-6 left-6 text-sm text-slate-400 hover:text-white flex items-center space-x-2 transition-colors duration-200 bg-slate-900/60 border border-slate-800 px-3 py-1.5 rounded-lg backdrop-blur-sm">
        <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke-width="2" stroke="currentColor"
            class="w-4 h-4">
            <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M10.5 19.5L3 12m0 0l7.5-7.5M3 12h18" />
        </svg>
        <span>Back to Map</span>
    </a>

    <!-- Container Card -->
    <div class="w-full mt-20 max-w-md bg-slate-900 border border-slate-800/80 rounded-2xl p-8 shadow-2xl relative z-10">

        <!-- Header Section -->
        <div class="text-center mb-6">
            <div
                class="inline-flex bg-emerald-500/10 p-3.5 rounded-2xl text-emerald-400 border border-emerald-500/20 mb-4 shadow-inner">
                <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke-width="2"
                    stroke="currentColor" class="w-8 h-8">
                    <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"
                        d="M12 9v6m3-3H9m12 0a9 9 0 11-18 0 9 9 0 0118 0z" />
                </svg>
            </div>
            <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-white tracking-tight">Create a New Room</h2>
            <p class="text-sm text-slate-400 mt-2">Initialize a secure tracking space for your network</p>
        </div>

        <!-- Form Submission -->
        <form action="/Map/create-room" method="POST" class="space-y-5">

            <!-- Room Name Input Field -->
            <div>
                <label for="roomName" class="block text-xs font-semibold text-slate-300 uppercase tracking-wider mb-2">
                    Room Identity / Name
                </label>
                <div class="relative">
                    <input type="text" id="roomName" name="roomName" required placeholder="e.g., Family-Home-Track"
                        class="w-full bg-slate-950 border border-slate-800 rounded-xl px-4 py-3 text-slate-200 placeholder-slate-600 focus:outline-none focus:border-emerald-500 focus:ring-2 focus:ring-emerald-500/20 transition-all duration-200 text-sm" />
                </div>
            </div>

            <!-- Action Button -->
            <button type="submit"
                class="w-full bg-emerald-600 hover:bg-emerald-500 active:bg-emerald-700 text-white font-semibold py-3 px-4 rounded-xl transition-all duration-150 text-sm shadow-lg shadow-emerald-900/20 hover:shadow-emerald-500/10 focus:outline-none focus:ring-2 focus:ring-emerald-500 focus:ring-offset-2 focus:ring-offset-slate-900 mt-2">
                Create Room
            </button>
        </form>

        <!-- Dynamic Context Info Panel -->
        <div
            class="mt-6 pt-4 border-t border-slate-850 flex items-start space-x-2.5 text-xs text-slate-500 leading-normal">
            <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke-width="1.5"
                stroke="currentColor" class="w-4 h-4 text-slate-400 shrink-0 mt-0.5">
                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"
                    d="M11.25 11.25l.041-.02a.75.75 0 011.063.852l-.708 2.836a.75.75 0 001.063.852l.041-.021M21 12a9 9 0 11-18 0 9 9 0 0118 0zm-9-3.75h.008v.008H12V8.25z" />
            </svg>
            <span>Creating a room generates an isolated environment where authorized family members can share
                coordinates natively.</span>
        </div>
    </div>

</body>

</html>